rows.label: tlk42100141_01_msg0001
rows.name: Do you know the name of this tree?

rows.label: tlk42100141_01_msg0002
rows.name:
The mercenaries here seem
to call it Valantia.

rows.label: tlk42100141_01_msg0003
rows.name: But its real name is Zozo's Tree.

rows.label: tlk42100141_01_msg0004
rows.name: Because you see, my name is Zozo.

rows.label: tlk42100141_01_msg0005
rows.name:
My father, and my father's father,
and his father before him must all
have been called Zozo too.
